This configuration provides:
Key Features:
Worker Pool Management — Automatic pooling with scheduler for concurrent processing
Language Auto-Detection — OSD (Orientation Script Detection) for unknown content
Vertical Text Support — Automatic handling of jpn_vert for traditional manga
Smart Caching — LRU cache to avoid re-processing identical regions
Manga-Specific Optimizations — PSM modes, noise filtering, inversion detection
Robust Error Handling — Retry logic with exponential backoff, custom error classes
Performance Monitoring — Built-in metrics collection
Integration Points:
Connects to your preprocessors/ modules (denoiser, binarizer, deskewer)
Works with postprocessors/ (manga-text-cleaner, bubble-classifier)
Uses performance-monitor.js from shared utils

Usage Example:

import { getTesseractManager } from './tesseract-config.js';

const ocr = getTesseractManager();
await ocr.initialize(['jpn', 'jpn_vert', 'kor']);

const result = await ocr.recognize(imageBlob, {
  language: 'auto',
  detectOrientation: true,
  region: { x: 100, y: 200, width: 300, height: 150 }
});